<template lang="pug">
    
</template>

<script>
    import $store from '../../components/store.js';

    export default {
        name: 'Modal',
        function(){
            return {}
        },
        computed: {
            modalVisible(){
                return this.$store.state.modalVisible;
            }
        },
        methods: {
            modalHidden(){
                this.$store.commit('modalVisible', false);
            }
        }
    }
</script>
